reviews.review_text: Sweet Spot was crowded  There are a few very nice audience captures for this show.  You can't go wrong with Stankiewicz tape or Wagners Nak 700's capture.  Gans' Sennheiser 421's get the nod (by a whisker).  Download and enjoy, this is a good one both show & sound.
